Long time back, in a thick and evergreen forest lived a monkey full of life and excitement.
On a bank of the river was a tree were the monkey lived on a beautiful tree with many branches on it.
The crocodile and his wife also lived on the other side of the lived.
Everyday, the monkey used to eat very dlicious and fulfilling fruits from the tree.
The crocodile used to watch him enjoy his meal from the other side. One day he deicded to go talk to the monkey.